bilingual.source: They practised carefully this week than last week.
bilingual.target: 他们这周比上周练习得更仔细。

bilingual.source: Say the seven days of the week.
I'm going to be away for a week in June.
My parents were away for a whole week.
So we started running a week ago.
bilingual.target: 所以我们一周前开始跑步。

bilingual.source: I use a calendar to plan my week.
bilingual.target: 我用日历来计划我的一周。

list.abstract: week（英[wiːk]，美[wiːk]），英语单词，名词，为星期；周；工作周。短语搭配有last week（上周）。例句为“And last week, they did it again.（上周，他们又这么做了。）”

yingyinNormal.en: You can't call me back for a week?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你整整一周都不回复我？

yingyinNormal.en: He'll be gone in a week. Oh, Harold!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他最多只能活一周了。哦，哈罗德！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: You should hire him, Finch, take the week off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你应该雇他，芬奇，休息一周。

yingyinNormal.en: Yep, tip your waitresses. I'm here all week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 给女服务生点小费，我这一周都在。

yingyinNormal.en: Taken a week ago. Diplomatic Security Service. Hobbs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周前拍的外交安全局是霍布斯。

yingyinNormal.en: It is one week later. Peppa, George, come and look.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周的时间过去了。佩奇，乔治，你们快来看。

yingyinNormal.en: It is one week later. Peppa, George, come and look.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周的时间过去了。佩奇，乔治，你们快来看。

yingyinNormal.en: Are they running it? No. I got a two-week delay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们已经在调查了吗？没有，我争取了延迟了两周。

yingyinNormal.en: All day long. Five days a week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 周一到周五，一天24小时。

yingyinNormal.en: One week in Abu Dhabi, all expenses paid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿布扎比一周游，所有费用全包。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm starting my own firm. When? Next week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我打算开家自己的律所。什么时候? 下周。

yingyinNormal.en: Take care, kid. You, too. See you next week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 保重，孩子。你也是，下周见。

yingyinNormal.en: And this week she sent 10-90s to Princeton, New Jersey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么本周他送10-90普林斯顿，新泽西州。

yingyinNormal.en: Went to Sam's grave every day. Then twice a week. Then once a week. I sought out therapy for myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每天都去山姆的墓前，后来一周去两次，再后来一周一次，我还给自己找了心理医生。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, well, he also said he was going out of town for a week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他还说他要出城一周。

yingyinNormal.en: This was taken a week ago. I'll see you out front.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一周前拍的，我去前门等你。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm a week and a half late, Randall, and I feel like crap.
yingyinNormal.zh: 迟了一周半，兰德尔，我感觉糟透了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll be back to check on Jane in a week. I look forward to it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周后我再来给简检查。我很期待。

yingyinNormal.en: And he sent you an e-mail about a week ago. Can you read it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他一周前给你发了封邮件，你能读一下吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And I hope that we can reschedule for later this week.
yingyinNormal.zh: 希望我们这周晚些时候能再重新安排个时间会面。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_family.mean: n. 星期；周；工作周；一周工作时间；七天的时间；工作日；七天之后

examination_example.sentence: Welcome to this <highlight>week</highlight>'s episode of Book Talk.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 欢迎来到本周的《书谈》节目。

examination_example.sentence: She stated she had heard rumors of stock burning but not specific cases until this <highlight>week</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她说，她听到过烧毁库存的传言，但直到本周才知道具体的案例。

examination_example.sentence: Last <highlight>week</highlight>, one operated by the taxi company Uber struck and killed a woman pushing her bicycle across a wide road in Arizona.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 上周，Uber出租车公司运营的一辆出租车在亚利桑那州撞死了一名推着自行车穿过宽阔马路的妇女。

examination_example.sentence: But in the end, we stayed for only two <highlight>weeks</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是最后，我们只呆了两个星期。

examination_example.sentence: He will meet his new manager in two <highlight>weeks</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 两周后他将会见他的新经理。

examination_example.sentence: I start my new job in two <highlight>weeks</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我两周后开始我的新工作。

examination_example.sentence: Are you free to come over for a coffee early next <highlight>week</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 下周初你有空过来喝杯咖啡吗？

examination_example.sentence: Why does the woman invite the man to her house next <highlight>week</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为什么女人下周邀请男人去她家？

examination_example.sentence: And last <highlight>week</highlight>, they did it again.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 上周，他们又这么做了。

examination_example.sentence: Learning to ride a bike is almost always more difficult for an adult, and this can take days and <highlight>weeks</highlight>, rather than hours.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于一个成年人来说，学习骑自行车几乎总是更加困难，这可能需要几天甚至几周的时间，而不是几个小时。

examination_example.sentence: Within <highlight>weeks</highlight>, her depression had begun to ease as she cycled.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几周之内，她的抑郁症随着骑自行车(这种运动)开始缓解。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes its employees are released from their daily jobs for <highlight>weeks</highlight>, and spend their time interacting in the innovation facility instead.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时，它的员工会从日常工作中解放出来几个星期，而是花时间在创新设施中互动。

direction_info.description:

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: It's been three <highlight>weeks</highlight> since he first started going, so Macy and I are pretty used to it now.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 距离他第一次离开已经有三周了，所以梅西和我现在已经很习惯了。

examination_example.sentence: Frozen bananas will last several <highlight>weeks</highlight>, depending on their ripeness and the temperature of the freezer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 冷冻香蕉可以保存几个星期，这取决于香蕉的成熟度和冰箱的温度。

examination_example.sentence: Depending on the kind of race you plan to enter, you can set up a timetable for the remaining <highlight>weeks</highlight> before the race.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据你计划参加的比赛类型，你可以在比赛前为剩下的几周制定时间表。

examination_example.sentence: In fact, I haven't got much sleep this past <highlight>week</highlight>, and I feel really tired.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实上，在过去的一周我睡得很少，感觉很累。

examination_example.sentence: Be sure to come back to work next <highlight>week</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 下周一定要回来工作。

examination_example.sentence: Compensating on the weekends actually feeds into your sleepiness the following <highlight>week</highlight>, a recent study found.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近的一项研究发现，在周末补觉实际上会加剧你下一周的睡意。

examination_example.sentence: During the first <highlight>week</highlight>, do not think about distance, but run five minutes longer each day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在第一个星期，不要考虑距离，而是每天多跑五分钟。
